Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:21.65,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The morning sun rises on the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.99,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Casting uncountable pillars of light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:31.54,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Each one leading to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:36.25,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Even if ten years turns into twenty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.79,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and the world still hasn't changed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:46.68,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We will never stop walking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:53.77,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Open the shining door and go straight through
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:20:01.40,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In front of you lay yet unknown mysteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:12.70,Massugu Yuku TL,insert,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}{\blur4}When our eyes meet, we seek the galaxy's mystery...
