Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Couldn't this be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Satoshi Nishizawa, 32 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Mechanic and engineer for the\Nimport car company, New Image.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:57.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A client, Kaori Yoda, asked the old man to find\Nout the identity of the stalker following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:01.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Through the investigation, the\Nstalker was found to be Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:07.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He received a court order to stay away from the client, and was dismissed from his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This case was two months ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's his address?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Fukagawa, Kōtō district.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's right near Ōyoko River!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's the flat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:22:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Looks like he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, stop, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you can't just\Nwalk into someone else's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.60,Dialogue,NEP,0,0,0,,{\blur1}While trying to find out what happened to the ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:03.68,Dialogue,NEP,0,0,0,,{\blur1}the suspect was found dead.
